{"tid":255413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"紅隧路線重組系列","createTime":"2017-05-24T01:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T17:30:31.000Z","uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce99951b185b8e434bacc698adefa494559d841","tid":255413,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:09:47.000Z","msg":"只重組九龍線, 新界線唔改動 (其實都得170同182系)<br />\n因為某巴打於此post (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/250164/page/8\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/250164/page/8</a>) 屌堆紅隧線, 我決定放呢堆建議上黎比佢同大家欣賞下<br />\n<br />\n1. 中西區篇: <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1A_mZFkCSX__R4d1HOj9OvQB6CmN1isKhWV2y2OMQJ4A/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1A_mZFkCSX__R4d1HOj9OvQB6CmN1isKhWV2y2OMQJ4A%2Fedit&d=bkmCab2tTnvP0lIxHnt1CJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=afde26d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1A_mZFkCSX__R4d1HOj9OvQB6CmN1isKhWV2y2OMQJ4A/edit</a><br />\n改動大綱:<br />\n1.103/104/113縮短<br />\n2.109改為兩繁服務, 其餘時間由113繞經何文田<br />\n3.103P改經彌敦道以測試客量<br />\n4.111調整班次配合302提升服務<br />\n5.302提升服務<br />\n6.101X不提升服務<br />\n<br />\n2. 灣仔區和東區篇: <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AkHNaAom1vsdYgkHZwn16wvNLgCDAFdViM1SGJZADcw/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1AkHNaAom1vsdYgkHZwn16wvNLgCDAFdViM1SGJZADcw%2Fedit&d=bkmCab2tTnvP0lIxHnt1CJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ab2acb6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AkHNaAom1vsdYgkHZwn16wvNLgCDAFdViM1SGJZADcw/edit</a><br />\n改動大綱:<br />\n1.102/106/112縮短<br />\n2.102P提升服務, 改稱102X<br />\n3.106港島方向改經渣華道<br />\n4.106A新增下繁服務, 106P改為兩繁雙向服務<br />\n5.110來回程不經北角並加強早繁往九龍服務, 北角特班改編至106<br />\n6.117調整班次和延長服務時間, 並與118對換紅隧往港島方向站位<br />\n7.117R取消, 由112取代<br />\n8.117P試辦, 由跑馬地前往長沙灣工業區<br />\n9.118C開辦, 由小西灣來往長沙灣工業區<br />\n10.118X開辦, 依788/789走線直達九龍<br />\n<br />\n3.南區篇 (建議涉及東隧線671): <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_pi1ai66QNmnZsdorNudoSeKT9KY-J4PjcK7IkvVlpU/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1_pi1ai66QNmnZsdorNudoSeKT9KY-J4PjcK7IkvVlpU%2Fedit&d=bkmCab2tTnvP0lIxHnt1CJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=779637d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_pi1ai66QNmnZsdorNudoSeKT9KY-J4PjcK7IkvVlpU/edit</a><br />\n建議大綱:<br />\n1.107延長至觀塘<br />\n2.107X開辦, 來往置富至觀塘, 並提供香港仔特快<br />\n3.671改經紅隧並改稱176, 同時縮減服務時間<br />\n4.107/107X新增與171/176之間的轉乘優惠<br />\n<br />\n有咩唔滿意盡情屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f7632c51d4940c2b94c80c92c52186d247dad8","tid":255413,"uid":33121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T01:12:32.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},{"pid":"ffde2191f3150baa8dc90450a3355359b0b4c953","tid":255413,"uid":78988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"671 keep番東隧 堅拿道後經維園道/東廊直接過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532c5f4c7fa25791f7dee79e82dd3d29a73f8a51","tid":255413,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>671 keep番東隧 堅拿道後經維園道/東廊直接過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔夠176快 (運吉同巴士公司已經測試過)<br />\n因為黃昏東隧東廊好塞 又唔似紅隧咁有巴士專線"}]}